snippet.title: Kaetram - Official Trailer (Beta)
snippet.description:
Kaetram is a 2D cross-platform pixel MMORPG. Adventure in a large world and discover quests, complete achievements, defeat bosses, and collaborate with others. We have 18 skills, 30 quests, over 100 achievements, and many bosses and areas to explore.

We are currently in the beta phases, expect to see much more content very soon!

Website: https://kaetram.com
Discord: https://discord.gg/kaetram
Play Store: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.kaetram.app&hl=en_IN
App Store: https://apps.apple.com/us/app/kaetram/id6468379072
Wiki: https://kaetram.fandom.com/wiki/Kaetram_Wiki
Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/kaetram
